        S10[HealthTech_PatientRecords]:::standard
        S11[HealthTech_PatientRecords]:::standard
        S12[HealthTech_LabAnalyzer]:::standard
        S13[HealthTech_PatientRecords]:::meeting

    %% STAGE 3: FINALIZATION
    subgraph Stage3[HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine]
        direction TB
        Stage3Title[HealthTech_PatientRecords]:::legendBox
        S14[HealthTech_LabAnalyzer]:::premium
        S15[HealthTech_EMR_Sync]:::premium

        S17[HealthTech_PatientRecords]:::standard
        S18[HealthTech_EMR_Sync]:::standard

    Legend -.-> Stage1
